definitions.definition: Of or relating to the Passeriformes order of perching birds , which are generally anisodactyl ( “ having three toes pointing forward and one back , which facilitates perching ” ) .
Chiefly in the former names of some birds : approximately the size of a sparrow .

main_definition: Of or relating to the Passeriformes order of perching birds , which are generally anisodactyl ( “ having three toes pointing forward and one back , which facilitates perching ” ) .
